description.plain:
Rihanna originally recorded “Answer” for her 2011 sixth studio album Talk That Talk, but it didn’t make the final cut for the album. It was rumored that Rihanna has recorded the song twice. The first time, for Talk That Talk. It seems Rihanna liked the song so much that after about three years, she re-recorded it in 2014 (supposedly for ANTI). The second one has an improved beat and new vocals.

However, Rihanna didn’t want this song on Talk That Talk for unknown reasons, and in November 2011 posted on Facebook: “DONE B**CHES!!!! #TTT Tracklist (EXCEPT "Answer” and NOT in sequence)“.



@RihannaStuffOFC leaked a 10 second snippet of the song on December 24, 2017. The full song leaked on April 4, 2018.

